OL,2,MLoRa from Space
OL,4,CAndrew Lindsay
OL,5,CSat 14:50-15:30
OL,6,CStage A
OL,8,GThis talk is about my personal
OL,9,Gexperience in assembling and testing
OL,10,Gthe satellite payloads as well as
OL,11,Gworking with LoRa based satellites. I
OL,12,Ghave so far assembled and tested 10
OL,13,Gpayloads that are installed in 6
OL,14,Gsatellites currently orbiting the
OL,15,Gearth. More payloads have been
OL,16,Gassembled and tested but not yet
OL,17,Glaunched. The talk will include plenty
OL,18,Gof photographs and a couple of short
OL,19,Gvideos covering the different stages
OL,20,Gof the build and testing. It goes
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
